---
import GlassCard from "./primitives/GlassCard.astro";
import Section from "./primitives/Section.astro";
import SectionHeader from "./primitives/SectionHeader.astro";
import { EVENT_URLS } from "../data/event";
---

<Section
  id="challenge"
  labelledBy="challenge-heading"
  width="narrow"
  padding="compact"
>
  <SectionHeader
    id="challenge-heading"
    title="The Challenge"
    subtitle="Build an AI proof-of-concept that modernizes Michigan industries and keeps opportunity here."
    align="center"
  />

  <GlassCard class="challenge-card" elevation="raised">
    <div class="challenge-inner">
      <div class="challenge-grid">
        <div class="challenge-problem">
          <p class="challenge-lede">
            Michigan stands at a pivotal moment. Once the undisputed engine of
            American innovation, our state is ready to reclaim its position as a
            technology leader—not by abandoning our industrial heritage, but by
            reimagining it for the 21st century.
          </p>
          <p class="challenge-body">
            While Michigan ranks among the top states in manufacturing output,
            we lag behind in technology adoption and digital transformation. Too
            often, our brightest minds leave for coastal tech hubs, and Michigan
            jobs get outsourced elsewhere. The question is simple: how do we use
            cutting-edge AI to modernize our cornerstone industries while
            building an ecosystem that makes Michigan a destination—not a
            departure point?
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="challenge-side">
          <h3 class="challenge-subtitle">The stats tell the story</h3>
          <ul class="challenge-list">
            <li>
              Michigan graduates leave the state at higher rates than most,
              seeking tech opportunities elsewhere
            </li>
            <li>
              Many legacy industries still operate with outdated systems and
              manual processes
            </li>
            <li>
              Small and medium-sized Michigan businesses cite technology
              adoption as their #1 barrier to growth
            </li>
            <li>
              Brain drain continues as innovators lack the infrastructure and
              community to build here
            </li>
            <li>
              Immense untapped potential in AI-driven innovation across
              manufacturing, supply chain, agriculture, sustainability,
              education, and urban development
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="challenge-divider" role="separator" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <h3 class="challenge-subtitle">What we’re asking you to build</h3>
      <p class="challenge-body">
        Using AI and open source technologies, build an innovative
        proof-of-concept solution that addresses one of these focus areas.
      </p>

      <ul class="challenge-focus">
        <li>
          <span class="challenge-focus-title"
            >Modernizing Michigan Manufacturing</span
          >
          <span class="challenge-focus-desc">
            AI-powered automation, predictive maintenance, quality control, or
            supply chain optimization that keeps production and jobs in
            Michigan.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="challenge-focus-title">Reinvigorating Main Street</span>
          <span class="challenge-focus-desc">
            Accessible AI tools for customer engagement, inventory management,
            market analysis, or operations that help small businesses compete
            without outsourcing.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="challenge-focus-title">Next-Gen Mobility</span>
          <span class="challenge-focus-desc">
            Autonomous systems, smart infrastructure, or connected vehicle
            technologies developed and deployed here.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="challenge-focus-title">Agricultural Innovation</span>
          <span class="challenge-focus-desc">
            AI-driven solutions for precision farming, sustainability, crop
            management, or food supply chain optimization.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="challenge-focus-title"
            >Building Michigan’s Innovation Ecosystem</span
          >
          <span class="challenge-focus-desc">
            Tools that help founders, developers, and communities collaborate,
            prototype, and scale ventures without leaving the state.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="challenge-focus-title"
            >Sustainability &amp; Clean Energy</span
          >
          <span class="challenge-focus-desc">
            Optimize energy use, monitor Great Lakes water quality, manage
            renewable grids, reduce waste, or accelerate Michigan’s transition
            to a greener economy.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="challenge-focus-title"
            >Education &amp; Workforce Development</span
          >
          <span class="challenge-focus-desc">
            Personalized tutoring, skills gap analysis, retraining platforms,
            career pathways, and expanded access across rural and urban
            Michigan.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="challenge-focus-title"
            >Smart Urban Planning &amp; Community Development</span
          >
          <span class="challenge-focus-desc">
            Smarter transit, infrastructure planning, neighborhood
            revitalization, public safety, housing data, and more responsive
            city services.
          </span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <aside class="sponsor-note" aria-label="Sponsor challenge opportunity">
        <strong>Sponsors:</strong> define a real AI challenge from your organization
        — teams build toward it all weekend, and winning projects demo at Michigan
        Tech Week (May 19–21).
        <a href={EVENT_URLS.sponsorInquiry}>Get in touch →</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </GlassCard>
</Section>

<style>
  .challenge-inner {
    padding: 1.75rem;
  }

  .challenge-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .challenge-lede {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.2vw, 1.35rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .challenge-body {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .challenge-subtitle {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .challenge-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .challenge-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .challenge-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: rgb(148 163 184 / 25%);
    margin: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  }

  .challenge-focus {
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .challenge-focus li {
    padding: 1.05rem 1.15rem;
    border: 1px solid rgb(148 163 184 / 18%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: rgb(15 23 42 / 45%);
  }

  .challenge-focus-title {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent-green);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .challenge-focus-desc {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (min-width: 64rem) {
    .challenge-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }
  }

  .sponsor-note {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent-orange);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
    background: rgb(251 191 36 / 6%);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .sponsor-note strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-orange);
  }

  .sponsor-note a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .sponsor-note a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
